template <typename Block, typename LP>
class vsip::impl::Low_level_data_access<Copy_access_tag,Block,LP>
File: ../../../vsip/core/extdata.hpp

Specialization for copied direct data access.

Template parameters:
Block:to be a block.
LP:is a layout policy describing the desired layout. The desired layout can be different from the block's layout.
Notes:
When the desired layout packing format is either Stride_unit or Stride_unknown, the packing format used will be Stride_unit_dense.
Primary template: Low_level_data_access
